long_description: The Chaco Dillan Shoes join the trusty underfoot support of Chaco sandals with the smooth styling of street-ready shoes so your feet stay comfortable even in the urban wilderness. Canvas and suede leather uppers provide durable, flexible support; tongue loops offer easy on/off. LUVSEAT(TM) X03 platform features thin-profile polyurethane midsoles, which provide superior arch support for all-day wear. Nonmarking Chaco EcoTread rubber outsoles contain 25% recycled rubber and offer excellent all-around traction. Closeout.
